sequenceDiagram
  %% Diagrama de secuencia FSD-UC-005 - Confirmar pago y emitir ticket QR
  autonumber
  participant U as Asistente
  participant BANK as Banco/Pasarela
  participant API as Core API
  participant SIG as Signature Verifier
  participant WRK as Worker emisión
  participant DB as PostgreSQL
  participant NOT as Notification Service

  U->>BANK: Paga con app bancaria
  BANK->>API: POST /webhooks/payments (firmado)
  API->>SIG: Verificar firma del proveedor
  SIG-->>API: válido
  API->>DB: Buscar orden por reference (lock)
  alt callback duplicado
    DB-->>API: ya confirmada
    API-->>BANK: 200 OK (idempotente)
  else nueva confirmación
    API->>DB: payment.status=confirmed; order.status=confirmed
    API->>WRK: job EmitTicket(orderId)
    WRK->>DB: Generar ticket(s) con qr_token firmado
    WRK->>NOT: Enviar ticket por email/WhatsApp
    NOT-->>U: Ticket entregado
    API-->>BANK: 200 OK
  end
